title: UPDATED APARTMENT FOR RENT IN COLLIERVILLE w/ pool
map_address: 325 S Center St near Rowlett St
app_fee: $60 application fee per adult for background, credit check and processing
posting_body: This renovated apartment unit is in a great neighborhood in Collierville.
It's down the street from the Old Town Square, where there's plenty of retail shopping and restaurants.
It's also not far from Highway 385, and not to mention the amazing Collierville school district.
The apartment comes with a community swimming pool, plenty of gated parking, on-site laundry facilities, central heat and air, and a very quiet and comfortable living space.
The unit is 850 sqft and has 2 beds and one bath.
The kitchen comes with all new cabinets, granite countertops, and all new appliances including a fridge, oven/range and dishwasher.
There's also brand new light fixtures, new paint, and new vinyl plank flooring throughout.
The bathroom has also been updated with new EVERYTHING!!
Come check it out before it's gone!
